   :match_1: statement|||A line of code that represents a command or action.
   :match_2: declaration|||A statement that creates a new variable and determines its type.
   :match_3: assignment|||A statement that assigns a value to a variable.
   :match_4: expression|||A combination of variables, operators and values that represents a single result value.

